name: Confirm that the selected conduit is of adequate size for purpose
It has been confirmed that all outlets/fittings in slab have been captured
Conduit has been securely fixed to the box or volcano
Conduit box has temporarily been secured and tied down in place for pour
Alternative route has been supplied in case main route is damaged
Conduit runs have all been marked on as builts
FINAL - Pass when happy to proceed with work(s) (Any issues please comment below)
